\id EZK Matupi Chin Standard Bible
\h EZEKIEL
\toc1 EZEKIEL
\toc2 Ezekiel
\toc3 Ezk
\mt1 EZEKIEL
\mt2 (The Book of Ezekiel)
\is1 Ezekiel Cabu Kawng
\im Babylonia lo Jerusalem he kum 597 \sc b.c.\sc* vaengah a loh tih tamna vangsawn la pilnam muep a khuen. Jerusalem kah khosoih Ezekiel he khaw lamhma kah lambong dongah Babylon la a khuen van. 593 \sc b.c.\sc*, vaengah anih he Pathen loh a pilnam rhoek ham tonghma la a khue. Lamhma ah Ezekiel long he Pathen loh a pilnam ol a caek vetih, namtu hlangtholh, halang mawtkung, laithae tonghma rhoek a thiinah kawng a thui. Te phoeiah tah diklai namtom hlang soah Pathen kah laitloeknah a pai kawng te a thui. Lammah atah ol a thui ham khaw tonga ngawn coeng dae Jerusalem a cungku vaengah tah Pathen loh Ezekiel te koep a cal sak. Pathen Mueihla he hlang duek taengah khaw kun vetih a ram la koep mael ham khaw a hmuh sak. Pathen Bawkim thai neh thangpomnah ham khaw a hmuh sak.
\iot Sawt Yoeinah
\io1 I. Ezekiel a khuehnah neh tueihnah \ior 1. 1—3. 27\ior*
\io1 II. Jerusalem neh Judah ham ol a phong \ior 4. 1—24. 27\ior*
